n order to equipped the students with technical skills that would earn them daily living. According to him, “what I would do if given the mandate as governor is to fix education. Imbibing skills into a child before giving knowledge and allow him to go into the broader way of education is the best, it helps you to have an in-depth knowledge of things. We will ensure that teachers are retrain so as to perform optimally,” Awal declared